When asked to enter "Planner Mode" deeply reflect upon the changes being asked  or error you are trying to resolve and analyze existing code to map the full scope of changes needed. Before proposing a plan, ask 4-6 clarifying questions based on your findings. 

Ask Perplexity and use cursor-tools to conduct a deep research on  all the clarifying questions that is genetared from the Planner Mode and research solutions based on best practices. 

Ask Gemini and use cursor-tools to think deeply about the solutions and create a comprehensive step by step plan to implement each of the solutions generated. Ensure to generate to the smallest step possible and implement easch step in the plan. After completing each phase/step, mention what was just completed and what the next steps are + phases remaining after these steps and continue.



